<br>
3000 plat sounds high though.  Wurmslayer has a little better ratio than Ceni SS, but it's slow as hell and weighs a ton.<br>
<br>
I'd recommend going up to Bazaar at night, and filtering by weapons you can use, and then just look at the stats on all of them.  Oftentimes you can find really good weapons priced low because they're restricted to 1 or 2 classes (I saw some kickass bard-only weapons for sale for like 500 plat).<br>
